    <item>
      <title>Version 1.5.2</title>
      <sparkle:version>11</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.5.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>10.15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <ul>
          <li>ClaudeBar can now update itself — a new "Check for Updates…" item in the menu, plus automatic daily background checks.</li>
        </ul>
